12.short_description: SWAPP is the first exchange community for employees that work at fast moving consumer goods companies

18.description:
SWAPP is the first exchange community for employees that work at fast moving consumer goods multinational companies where users can generate significant monthly savings by exchanging the products they obtain as a benefit (with discount or for free) in their corporations. The employees benefit each other while also generating greater brand exposure and less waste for their organizations.
We provide a 360º solution. 
On one hand, SWAPP helps users to take the most out of the products that they receive with discount (or for free) at their companies but they no longer need or use due to the diminishing marginal utility law. Instead of accumulating those products at home, they can now exchange them for new and different products from other brands, and save in the supermarket bill in an inflation context.
While we also help the companies to increase their employees’ satisfaction and in the meantime to “get rid of” products in a new channel (for those products with a short expiration date or damaged and/or old-dated packaging).
Our customers are the Fast Moving Consumer Goods Companies that want to increase their employees general satisfaction, by providing them the possibility of becoming users at SWAPP to exchange the products they no longer use/need to receive new products they have selected from their counterparts.
